<br>
I get back online and discover that there was an argument between 2 people and that all the 50+ people but myself left the guild and joined another guild... including the GL who disbanded the guild. I didn't even know of this till after the fact... and I was a fooking officer.<br>
<br>
So, everything was fine then I take a short break from the game to find our guild, one of the oldest on the server had been disbanded and most members joining another guild.<br>
<br>
/shrug.<br>
